sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Customer
    participant S as NanoSoft Store
    participant J as Jaib API

    C->>S: Enter purchase code, mobile, amount
    S->>J: LogAPI request (userName, password, agentCode)
    J-->>S: accessToken, pinApi
    S->>J: ExeBuy request (pinApi, mobile, requestID, code, amount, currencyCode)
    J-->>S: referenceID, msg
    S->>S: Update order state to Paid
    S-->>C: Payment success notification